        </Card>
        <Card as="article" variant="outline">
          <h3>^ ‚ÄúTo the Power Of‚Äù</h3>
          <p>Amplification through shared knowledge and collaboration.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card as="article" variant="outline">
          <h3>‚ö° ‚ÄúPlasma Arc‚Äù</h3>
          <p>The energetic bridge between matter and air ‚Äî symbolising transformation.</p>
        </Card>
      </div>

      <p class="reflection-text center">
        arc^ = resistance √ó regeneration √ó plasma energy  
        <br />ArcUp is both metaphor and method ‚Äî a spark that rises, connects, and transforms.
      </p>
      <!-- üí¨ Claude: could use animated caret glyph or subtle electric glow underline here for motion. -->
    </section>

    <SectionDivider variant="default" spacing="normal" />

    <!-- ================================================================ -->
    <!-- SECTION 4 ‚Äî The ArcUp Phases -->
    <!-- ================================================================ -->
    <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="phases-title">
      <SectionHeader
        title="The ArcUp Phases ‚Äî From Spark to Commons"
        subtitle="How individual curiosity becomes collective capability."
        align="center"
      />

