            This phase builds a commons of plasma tools where knowledge circulates responsibly and safely.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <Card as="article" variant="surface">
          <h3>üî≠ Phase 3 ‚Äî Collaborative Application</h3>
          <p>
            Interdisciplinary teams and institutions co-develop plasma systems in real-world contexts.  
            Governance shifts from ownership to custodianship ‚Äî ensuring discoveries remain open for all.
          </p>
        </Card>
      </div>

      <CalloutPanel variant="neutral" icon="üß≠" title="Our Direction">
        <p>
          ArcUp‚Äôs progress isn‚Äôt measured by products but by participation ‚Äî 
